Enum NotePlacement

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<NotePlacement>
      • org.nasdanika.diagram.NotePlacement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<NotePlacement>, Enumerator

    public enum NotePlacement
extends Enum<NotePlacement>
implements Enumerator
    A representation of the literals of the enumeration 'Note Placement', and utility methods for working with them. Note placement for diagram elements. Ignored for connections.
    See Also:
